Warren Eric Rosser (born 2 October 1962) is an Australian judoka. He competed in the men's half-lightweight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. He has two sons, Michael Rosser, a Sydney-based Senior Wills and Estate Planning Consultant, and Tom Rosser, a Melbourne-based Psychologist.
